data.description: BRAND NEW CARPET!!! Assumable 5.99% rate. Below appraised value! Lovely 4/ 5 w/ bonus, 3.5 BA home in sought after Halle Plantation in Collierville, TN. This home boast a large entry way with hardwood floors throughout the living areas, open kitchen, granite countertops, home office, 2 fireplaces, 2 on-suite BRs. Laundry room, 3 car garage with additional parking pad, large fenced backyard with outdoor pergola, new HVAC, new Sprinkler System. Community pool, play yard, lakes, & 2 clubhouses.
